---
title: Smoked salmon pasta
introduction: Jamie's smoked salmon pasta with spinach, spring onion, lemon, curds & Parmesan is quick and easy.
image: https://asset.jamieoliver.com/images/cq7w2e71/production/440f5e61b2e2f165dbd45f3218e0b352c3e26135-958x1280.jpg/136295675?rect=0,161,958,958&w=600&h=600&fm=webp&q=75&fit=crop&auto=format
